    "title": "Ahadi ya Kutoka kwa Pili",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "ahadi ya kutoka kwa pili",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Mungu aliwarudisha watu wa Israeli kwenye nchi yao kutoka Babuloni, kama alivyowatoa Misri miaka mingi iliyopita (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:20-Isa48:21\">Isaya 48:20–21</a>). (Uokoaji huu wa kwanza kutoka Misri unaitwa Kutoka.) Wakati huu, walipoondoka Babuloni, watu walihitaji kuwa safi na kuchukua muda wao, bila haraka ya kuondoka (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:11\">52:11</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:12\">,12</a>).</p><p>Uzoefu wa uhamishoni na safari unafananishwa na jangwa ambalo Bwana huokoa (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:1\">Isaya 35:1</a>):</p><ul><li><p>Anatengeneza barabara kupitia jangwa na kulibadilisha kuwa mahali penye maji, mimea, na wanyama (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:19-Isa43:20\">Isaya 43:19–20</a>).</p></li><li><p>Anatoa njia za kuondoa vikwazo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:16\">42:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:11\">49:11</a>).</p></li><li><p>Anawaongoza watu wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:16\">42:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:11\">58:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:13\">63:13</a>).</p></li><li><p>Wanawalisha (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:10\">49:10</a>).</p></li><li><p>Anawalinda dhidi ya joto (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:10\">49:10</a>).</p></li><li><p>Anawapa nguvu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:11\">58:11</a>).</p></li><li><p>Anabadilisha huzuni yao kuwa furaha kubwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:3\">51:3</a>).</p></li><li><p>Anamimina Roho Wake juu yao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:3-Isa44:4\">44:3–4</a>).</p></li></ul><p>Wakristo pia hupitia &quot;Kutoka.&quot; Wanaacha dhambi na kifo nyuma kupitia kifo na ufufuo wa Yesu. Roho Mtakatifu huwasaidia Wakristo kuishi maisha mapya. Wanamtumikia Mungu kwa furaha huku wakingoja ufalme wake ufike kikamilifu.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:8-Isa35:10\">Isaya 35:8–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:14-Isa42:16\">42:14–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:18-Isa43:21\">43:18–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:3-Isa44:4\">44:3–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:20-Isa48:21\">48:20–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:9-Isa49:12\">49:9–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:11-Isa52:12\">52:11–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:8-Isa58:12\">58:8–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:2-Jer31:17\">Yeremia 31:2–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:17-Joel3:21\">Yoeli 3:17–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:78-Luke1:79\">Luka 1:78–79</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:38\">Yohana 7:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:19\">15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:17\">2 Wakorintho 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:17-2Cor6:18\">6:17–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:8\">Waefeso 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:13\">Wakolosai 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:12-Heb13:14\">Waebrania 13:12–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:16\">Ufunuo 7:16</a></p>",
